-- Italy's Cavalli in exclusive talks with Clessidra 
-- 
-- Wed Dec 17, 2014 02:18PM EST
-- None



MILAN, Dec 17 (Reuters) - Italian fashion brand Roberto Cavalli is in exclusive talks with Clessidra that would give the private equity firm a majority stake in the label, Clessidra said in a statement on Wednesday.

The companies have set a target to reach an accord by March 2015.